{
    "description": "The data source \"source9\" contains clinical data from the study \"Proteogenomic characterization of pancreatic ductal adenocarcinoma\" by Cao, L. et al. The dataset, accessible at https://ars.els-cdn.com/content/image/1-s2.0-S0092867421009971-mmc1.xlsx, includes patient information such as demographic details, medical history, tumor characteristics, and follow-up outcomes, stored in a table named \"Cao.csv\".",
